/>恨食人血饅頭恨到出曬面咁</strong>。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">無like，係因為你唔值得被like</span></span>，剩係識拋對波出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲相又唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />齋filter都出曬事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人又無內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點like丫？KOL？俾啲自知之明啦，憑咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">想食人血饅頭借抗爭上位？仆街死啦你</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">懶咩清高姐你</span></span>，咩唔買like丫乜乜柒柒，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你只係用「捐錢換like」代替「買like」</strong></span>姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你同佢地係一撚樣嫁咋&hellip;&hellip;同啲ptgf話自己唔係雞因為有權say no有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出賣肉體就出賣肉體啦。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">雞就雞啦！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最睇唔起食人血饅頭既人，你咁想出位，我幫下你囉"},{"pid":"a6cbf29717ec07b84676eede606f8fbbf0903fe5","tid":1791432,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T21:34:31.000Z","msg":"之前有個乜乜痴線post定係痴線拎定乜春咁上下啦<br />\n專追擊啲美容乞兒 辣殺KOL 冇一條女個樣係叫得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e859c34cac1a01e19949ee6caf12f6fe5ae244","tid":1791432,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T22:07:50.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家多謝特朗普，學加拿大咁樣搭單，希望中國口頭承諾比香港普選<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread